OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FFurther rain and strong winds on
OL,7,FWednesday with some showers on
OL,8,FThursday. Brighter with fewer showers
OL,9,Fon Friday. Feeling a little warmer
OL,10,Fthan of late, especially in any
OL,11,Fsunshine.
